@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dlrqcv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.89)))
    v2 = ((0.90 - 0.82) - wp.exp(v0))
    v1 = 0.98
    tmp = v2
    v0 = v2
    v1 = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = (wp.exp(v1) * (v1 - v0))
    data[tid] = v0
